quran[9{c,v,t}:
7,179,"aur yeh haqeeqat hai ke bohat se jin aur ensaan aisay hain jin ko hum ne jahannum hi ke liye peda kya hai un ke paas dil hain magar woh un se sochte nahi un ke paas ankhen hain magar woh un se dekhte nahi un ke paas kaan hain magar woh un se suntay nahi woh janwaron ki terhan hain balkay un se bhi ziyada gay guzray, yeh woh log hain jo ghaflat mein kho ye gay hain"
7,180,"Allah achay naamon ka mustahiq hai, is ko achay hi naamon se poukaro aur unn logon ko chore do jo is ke naam rakhnay mein raasti se munharif ho jatay hain jo kuch woh karte rahay hain is ka badla woh paker rahen ge"
7,181,hamari makhlooq mein aik giroh aisa bhi hai jo theek theek haq ke mutabiq hadaayat aur haq hi ke mutabiq insaaf karta hai
7,182,"rahay woh log jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko jhutla diya hai, to inhen hum batadreej aisay tareeqa se tabahi ki taraf le jayen ge ke inhen khabar taq nah hogi"
7,183,"mein un ko dheel day raha hon, meri chaal ka koi toar nahi hai"
7,184,aur kya inn logon ne kabhi socha nahi? inn ke Rafeeq par junoon ka koi assar nahi hai woh to aik khabardaar hai jo ( bura injaam samnay anay se pehlay ) saaf saaf mutnabba kar raha hai
7,185,kya un logon ne aasman o zameen ke intizam par kabhi ghhor nahi kya aur kisi cheez ko bhi jo khuda ne peda ki hai ankhen khol kar nahi dekha? aur kya yeh bhi unhon ne nahi socha ke shayad inn ki mohlat zindagi poori honay ka waqt qareeb aa laga ho? phir aakhirPeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamki iss tanbeeh ke baad aur konsi baat aisi ho sakti hai jis par yeh imaan layein ?
7,186,"jis ko Allah rahnumai se mahroom kar day uss ke liye phir koi rehnuma nahi hai, aur Allah aِnhin inn ki sar kashi hi mein bhatakta howa chhorey deta hai"
7,187,"yeh log tum se puchhte hain ke aakhir woh qayamat ki gharri kab nazil hogi? kaho"" is ka ilm mere rab hi ke paas hai ussay apne waqt par wohi zahir kere ga asmano aur zameen mein woh bara sakht waqt hoga woh tum par achanak aa jaye ga"" yeh log is ke mutaliq tum se is terhan puchhte hain goya ke tum is ki khoj mein lagey hue ho kaho"" is ka ilm to sirf Allah ko hai magar aksar log is haqeeqat se na waaqif hain """
